definition: contrary/in reverse/inside out or upside down/to reverse/to return/to oppose/opposite/against/anti-/to rebel/to use analogy/instead/abbr. for 反切[fan3 qie4] phonetic system

sentences.english: If we minimize rise time we increase overshoot, and viceversa.
sentences.chinese: 如果我们减少上升时间，也就增加了过冲，反之亦然。

sentences.english: And vice-a-versa, all at the perfect pace.
sentences.chinese: 反之亦然，一切都以完美的步调进行。

sentences.english: Energy transmutes into matter and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 能量变成物质，反之亦然。

sentences.english: Scrolling past the last item will take you to the first item in the list and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 则滚过最后一项后将到达列表的第一项，反之亦然。

sentences.english: The one controlling the results of the other, and viceversa.
sentences.chinese: 一方掌控着另一方的结果，反之亦然。

sentences.english: The more you select, the more proposals you will be alerted to and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 选择的越多，您将收到越多提案的通知，反之亦然。

sentences.english: Where light is – there is no place for shadow and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 有光的地方就无影，反之亦然。

sentences.english: The way he plays really brings the best out of me and vice-versa.
sentences.chinese: 他踢球的风格使我能够发挥最佳状态，反之亦然。

sentences.english: On the source, the GREater the damage, but also affected the scope of the smaller, and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 震源越浅，破坏越大，但波及范围也越小，反之亦然。

sentences.english: When one side wins, the other loses, and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 一方赢则意味着另一方输，反之亦然。

sentences.english: The thermoelectric effect is the direct conversion of temperature differences to electric voltage and vice-versa.
sentences.chinese: 热电效应能将温差直接转换成电压，反之亦然。

sentences.english: Any term in the singular applies to the pluraland vice-versa.
sentences.chinese: 一切使用单数的措辞同样适用于复数，反之亦然。

sentences.english: This can make genetically male plants produce female flowers and vice versa.
sentences.chinese: 这可能导致遗传上雄性的植物产生雌花，反之亦然。
